{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-004__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-004", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·004.1", "text_original": "鳧鷖在涇，公尸來燕來寧。爾酒既清，爾殽既馨。公尸燕飲，福祿來成。", "text_normalized": "鳧鷖在涇，公尸來燕來寧。爾酒既清，爾殽既馨。公尸燕飲，福祿來成。", "notes": "鳬鷖 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-004", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·004.2", "text_original": "鳧鷖在沙，公尸來燕來宜。爾酒既多，爾殽既嘉。公尸燕飲，福祿來為。", "text_normalized": "鳧鷖在沙，公尸來燕來宜。爾酒既多，爾殽既嘉。公尸燕飲，福祿來為。", "notes": "鳬鷖 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-004__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-004", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·004.3", "text_original": "鳧鷖在渚，公尸來燕來處。爾酒既湑，爾殽伊脯。公尸燕飲，福祿來下。", "text_normalized": "鳧鷖在渚，公尸來燕來處。爾酒既湑，爾殽伊脯。公尸燕飲，福祿來下。", "notes": "鳬鷖 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-004__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-004", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·004.4", "text_original": "鳧鷖在潀，公尸來燕來宗。既燕于宗，福祿攸降。公尸燕飲，福祿來崇。", "text_normalized": "鳧鷖在潀，公尸來燕來宗。既燕于宗，福祿攸降。公尸燕飲，福祿來崇。", "notes": "鳬鷖 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-shengmin-004__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-shengmin-004", "source_id": "daya-shengmin-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·生民之什·004.5", "text_original": "鳧鷖在亹，公尸來止熏熏。旨酒欣欣，燔炙芬芬。公尸燕飲，無有後艱。", "text_normalized": "鳧鷖在亹，公尸來止熏熏。旨酒欣欣，燔炙芬芬。公尸燕飲，無有後艱。", "notes": "鳬鷖 Chinese stanza 5."}
